{
  "stem": "1160.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she said, you know, you have this mirror furniture-- because this is one piece, the whole thing was one piece-- and this is mine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would like to have it back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This woman started to Jew her down, called her every kind of horrible names, just didn't hit her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother says, after all the suffering, everything what I went through, and I am not OK yet, and for a piece of furniture, I'm going to put myself through again such a horror?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even if I would sleep on the floor and everybody else, no furniture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way we are going to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not going to go to anybody anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's what we find when we came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Physical, we weren't so OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Physical, we were pretty run down, very skinny, bony, especially one of my younger brothers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- his suffering with that hunger, it just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he was hungry in the lager, you could see through his ear-- this part of the ear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But completely, like a-- like a pink light, reddish-pink light.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the saliva was coming from his mouth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how hungry he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we got a little bit of food-- and we were all very, very hungry-- the first thing all of us, me too, the first bite, Tibor got it, because the-- because the way he suffered, nobody-- and we all suffered, but his was terrible.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was heartbreaking to see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, myself, I was-- I had open wounds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had such a pus coming out, mostly from the joints of my body.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this time already, the Joint supply that's also for-- you know, that we can go to this doctor--",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
